                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>THE BATTLE-FIELD.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>They dropped like flakes, they dropped like stars,</l>
                    <l> Like petals from a rose,</l>
                    <l>When suddenly across the June</l>
                    <l> A wind with fingers goes.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>They perished in the seamless grass, </l>
                    <l> No eye could find the place;</l>
                    <l>But God on his repealless list</l>
                    <l> Can summon every face.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
